quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,89,"Nde Alla addi e ma…ì…ìe Kur'aan Teddunde nde, ende hawri e lasli cellu…ói gon…ói e Tawreeta e Injjil, tawii ko adii jippagol mayre e…ìe mbi'annoo: maa min poolu heefer…ìe …ìe, min udditanee so annabi nulaama min ngoon…óina mo min ndewa mo, nde Kur'aan o e Muhammadu (jkm) ngari e ma…ì…ìe, no …ìe nganndiri …óum e goonga; ndeen …ìe njeddi, hu…óoore Alla yo won e dow heefer…ìe yeddu…ìe Alla e nulaa…óo Makko."
  2,90,"Bone wonii e ko …ìe coodiri ko'e ma…ì…ìe (mbarjaari) …ìe njeddi ko Alla jippini …ìe penni Nulla…ìe Makko, …óum woni too√±e e nga√±gu sabu jippineede Annabaagal e Kur'aana o dow Muhammadu (jkm), e sabaabu ko …ìe ngadii waylitde e Tawreeta. Lette koynooje √±ande darnga na woodani …ìeen yeddu…ìe annabaagu Muhammadu (jkm)."
  2,91,"So tawii ∆Åee Yahuud…ìe mbi'aama: goon…óinee goonga e peewal ko Alla jippini dow Nulaa…óo Makko, …ìe mbi'a: mi…óen ngoon…óini ko jippinaa dow annabaa…ìe amen, …ìe njedda ko jippinaa dow Muhammadu (jkm), tawa noon ko oo Kur'aan woni goonga jahdu…óo e ko …ìe njogii ko, tawno …ìe ngoon…óinii ko jippinaa e ma…ì…ìe maa …ìe ngoon…óin Kur'aana o. Wii …ìe -Aan annabi-: ko wa…ói o…óon mbarannoo Annabaa…ìe Alla …ìe so tawno o…óon ngoon…óini goonga gar…óo e mon o?!"
  2,92,"Goonga tigi Nulaa…óo mon Muusaa (Jkm) addanii on maandeeji laa…ì…ói tinndinooji goon…óugol makko; …ìaawo …óuum o…óon ndewa ngaari ndi caggal nde Muusaa yahi nootoyaade joomum, onon ko on too√±oo…ìe o…óon ndenndina Alla e go…ó…óo, te ko Kanko tan haandi e reweede."
  2,93,"Ciftoree nde Min …ìami e mon aadi teentu…óo njokkon Muusaa kisal won e makko, e ja…ìde ko o addi iwde e Alla, Min …ìamti dow mon fello ngo ngam hul…ìinde on, Min mbii on: njogoree Tawreeta nde Min ngaddani on nde e soobee e tii…ónaare, nanee nja…ìon …óofto-…óon, si …óuum alaa Min li…ìa fello ngo dow moo…óon, mbii-…óon: min nanirii noppi amen min ngoopiri golle amen, rewde ngaari ndi debbi e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe sabu yeddugol ma…ì…ìe. Yo a wii …ìe - Aan Annabi-: bone wonii e …óum ko goon…óingol mon yamiri on keefeeru, so tawii o…óon ngoon…óini; sabu keefeeru yahdataa e goon…óinal goonga."